                     <hi rend="largeCaps">CHARLES DRAYLOG</hi> (56)</persName>
                  <rs id="t18640815-786-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18640815-786-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18640815-786-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>, Stealing a coat, the property of <persName id="t18640815-name-206" type="victimName">
